I am able to connect to Amazon Workspaces in my repro environment.  I have DPI enabled.  However, I also have Stealthy DPI enabled.

The first thing we need to do is understand if enabling stealthy DPI solves the problem.  If not then we need to understand other configuration differences.

[DevOps CommentId:10751106]
